{"tid":1020433,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[A/I] 結城友奈是勇者 - 花結的閃耀 - 召喚所有勇者部員","createTime":"2019-02-13T15:02:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T09:40:40.000Z","uid":159216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"446bd1226fd6cda9a737b035d5412e8ba5baddc4","tid":1020433,"uid":159216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T15:02:23.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eBbydrA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeBbydrA.jpg&h=227962b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結城友奈是勇者 - 花結的閃耀 (結城友奈は勇者である 花結いのきらめき)<br />\n遊戲類型 : 塔防遊戲<br />\n對應OS : Android／iOS<br />\n價格 : ITEM課金制<br />\n生產商 : KADOKAWA／オルトプラス／scopes<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4A35Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4A35Q.jpg&h=94465825&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nGoogle : <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.co.altplus.yuyuyui\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Djp.co.altplus.yuyuyui&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=907d4ac0\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=jp.co.altplus.yuyuyui</a><br />\nIOS : <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1205424282\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fapp%2Fid1205424282&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=aa929967\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1205424282</a><br />\nQOO : <a href=\"https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/5004\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.qoo-app.com%2Fapp%2F5004&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=16da618c\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/5004</a><br />\nPC版 : <a href=\"http://www.dmm.com/netgame/feature/yuyuyui.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dmm.com%2Fnetgame%2Ffeature%2Fyuyuyui.html&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=0b5c41bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dmm.com/netgame/feature/yuyuyui.html</a><br />\n<br />\n遊戲官方twitter : <a href=\"https://twitter.com/yyyi_game\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fyyyi_game&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=a19ae7b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/yyyi_game</a><br />\n系列官網 : <a href=\"http://yuyuyu.tv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyuyuyu.tv&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=e87cade6\" target=\"_blank\">http://yuyuyu.tv</a><br />\n系列官方twitter : <a href=\"https://twitter.com/anime_yukiyuna\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fanime_yukiyuna&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=dce1f249\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/anime_yukiyuna</a><br />\n新CM : <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fytdHVRUBZw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfytdHVRUBZw&d=uNZXw00WsTXXX%2FAwV3JyEZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=7d0ac736\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fytdHVRUBZw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">登場作品/人物 : </span><br />\n結城友奈是勇者<br />\n鷲尾須美是勇者<br />\n乃木若葉是勇者<br />\n楠芽吹是勇者<br />\n原創角色 : 秋原雪花、古波藏棗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">花結閃耀故事背景 :</span><br />\n讚州中學勇者部結城友奈等六人，<br />\n有一天課外活動時突然被不思議的光包圍，<br />\n醒來的時候發現已經置身樹海化的世界，而且vertex正進攻過來，<br />\n手中出現了本來已經不需要的變身app，<br />\n帶著疑惑同時把vertex擊退了的勇者部面前，<br />\n出現了一位自稱上里日向的女性。<br />\n <br />\n根據日向的講法，這裡是神樹內部的『特別世界』<br />\n神樹本來是多位土地神的集合體，<br />\n在多位土地神中的其位一個強力的土地神，在神樹的內部發起了叛亂<br />\n剛才的vertex就是造反神創造出的偽vertex，<br />\n因為土地神正處於四分五裂的狀態，神樹已經失去了大部份力量<br />\n<br />\n因此，神樹把不同時代的勇考召喚到自己之中<br />\n跨越時代的不同勇者結集於此，<br />\n造反神平定之戰現在開始...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oE2JAHc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoE2JAHc.jpg&h=a9f62e96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nUMFCU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnUMFCU3.jpg&h=d06663a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"1cfea44d7769dffed08a0e6e28ee5c571c5682e0","tid":1020433,"uid":159216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T15:03:16.000Z","msg":"仲有無生還者<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a4738f18a5e1a4a6bf83398beec13c909fd2d5","tid":1020433,"uid":159216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T15:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bcdd5e1c934e7c40f3dce12176a5bc3493ca85b","tid":1020433,"uid":159216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T15:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港已經無人玩"},{"pid":"9bddf9b7b388952049d1843168b6fac249189803","tid":1020433,"uid":13901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bcdd5e1c934e7c40f3dce12176a5bc3493ca85b","tid":1020433,"uid":159216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T15:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港已經無人玩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T16:42:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"970a79de2118774c9af354421c06671a0fe491e2","tid":1020433,"uid":159216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bddf9b7b388952049d1843168b6fac249189803","tid":1020433,"uid":13901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bcdd5e1c934e7c40f3dce12176a5bc3493ca85b","tid":1020433,"uid":159216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T15:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港已經無人玩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T16:42:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019